This is the geomtools package ChangeLog

2008-12-10 : creation by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>

2011-02-21 : Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* add placement::relocate method
2011-02-22 : Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* GPL version 3 is now used for geomtools
2011-03-19  Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* need datatools 3.0
2011-07-01 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* explicit linking with dependency shared libs
	* pre-tag 2.1
2012-01-06 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* pre-version: 3.0.0
	* cmake: new build system
	* FSH: new directory structure (as in datatools 4 and mygsl 3)
	* pkgtools.d: wrapper for cmake
2012-03-20 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* version: prepare tag 3.1.0 in trunk
	* depends: mygsl >=3.1
	* remove all "using namespace std;" from header files
2012-03-31 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* blut_spot: new class + associated serialization stuff
2012-04-05 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* spherical_extrusion_box_model: new class
	* spherical_extrusion_cylinder_model: new class
	* plate_with_hole_model: new class
	* gnuplot_draw : enrich box display with additional option
	* geomtools_check_setup.cxx : improve/fix
2012-04-09 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* bug fix: do not use the global static model creator db from i_model
	  because it does not work on gcc 4.6.X.
	  construct-on-first-use idiom : use a static scoped_ptr from within a static member function.
	  to be checked.
2012-10-08 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* add compute_barycenter and compute_weighted_barycenter functions
	* add class plane
	* improve support for tessellated solid
2012-11-04 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* add serializable display_data class
	* add i_wires_3d_rendering interface
	* version: prepare tag 3.2.0 in trunk
2012-11-29 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* fix bug in helix_3d::get_length()
	* version: prepare tag 3.2.1 in trunk
2013-02-24 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* version: prepare tag 4.0.0 in trunk
	* depend on: datatools pre-5.0.0 (datatools/trunk)
	* add geometry "manager" class (moved from sngeometry)
	* add geometry plugin support in the manager class
	* add system factory support for manager's geometry plugin
	* add "mapping_plugin" class
2013-03-09 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* add "geometry_service" class (from sncore)
2013-03-11 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* depends on materials 4.X
	* add "grid_model" class
	* add "materials_plugin" class
	* add "materials_utils" stuff (GDML export)
2013-04-24 : by Francois Mauger <mauger@lpccaen.in2p3.fr>
	* partial OCD support
	* support explicit unit at parsing of real properties
